    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 997.2 Carrera S is a concours-level example of the celebrated 9A1 power plant architecture. Featuring the 3.8L Direct Fuel Injection (DFI) flat-six, this unit delivers 385 hp through a crisp 6-speed manual transaxle. The mechanical integrity is absolute, with the Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) providing precise damping control and a factory-spec limited-slip differential ensuring optimal power delivery. The chassis remains rigid and the undercarriage is remarkably clean, showing no signs of heat cycling wear or fluid seepage. Equipped with the factory Sport Exhaust (PSE) for an unrestricted acoustic profile, this vehicle has been maintained with zero regard for cost, preserving its factory tolerances and tactile feedback. A rare find for the collector seeking the final iteration of the analog 911 experience.",
